Manually Install Plugin  If you want to take full control of the plugin, you can manually install the plugin by adding the following code to your   nuxt.config.js  file.     defineNuxtConfig  ({
   modules: [  'vue-recaptcha/nuxt'  ],
   runtimeConfig: {
